 />\n有少少位唱到opera feel<br />\n老屎忽都咁畀心機做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n閻奕格瘋狂carry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n胡琳都正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n譚耀文就喜出望外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n估唔到咁唱得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最on9係套野之前宣傳<br />\n搵佢拍個時裝八十年代mv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好趕客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入到場扮返無名成件事fit晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成場野好多野都睇得出畀咗好多心機<br />\nDancer 嘅舞、勁多衫<br />\n視覺效果設計（backdrop 、燈光）<br />\n聲效<br />\n道具<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最想投訴係鄭嘉穎把聲<br />\n同埋孔慈個陣味太濃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出味個陣d人瘋狂掩鼻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e068f36d80846048700fdd7c0bd56d17e3cc9cb","tid":189584,"uid":44761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T16:06:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除咗 21800000 把聲爛d<br />\n<br />\n一開波旦哥同柴九未入局頭兩首麻麻<br />\n<br />\n其他都ok<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呂良偉令我眼前一亮<br />\nD歌聽得出下咗好多苦功<br />\n有少少位唱到opera feel<br />\n老屎忽都咁畀心機做<img src=\"/asset